             was indicted for <rs id="t17990220-21-off105" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17990220-21-off105" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990220-21-off105" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17990220-21-cd106" type="crimeDate">4th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990220-21-off105 t17990220-21-cd106"></join>, 19lbs. weight of bacon, value 9s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17990220-21-victim203" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Crisp
               <interp inst="t17990220-21-victim203" type="surname" value="Crisp"></interp>
