                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990220-21-defend202 t17990220-21-punish111"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice ROOKE.</p>
